Package interactr.cs.kuleuven.be.ui

Interface DiagramObserver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CommunicationView, DiagramView, SequenceView, SubWindow

    public interface DiagramObserver
    An interface for diagram observers. Each diagram observer is notified of changes to the diagram that it observes. Each change is of a certain type, each type of update has a specific set of parameters.
